52
00:04:03,440 --> 00:04:08,100
No. I just thought
since I edit her column I...

53
00:04:08,140 --> 00:04:11,600
And this matters to me
because...

54
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:11,800
Precisely.

55
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:13,700
I'll need the next column myself.

56
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:15,900
And for God sakes, clean yourself up.

57
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:20,600
You should totaly be writing
that intro. You know.

58
00:04:20,640 --> 00:04:24,900
You know Belinda better than
anyone and you're an amazing writer.

59
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:25,200
Thanks.

60
00:04:25,400 --> 00:04:28,300
It's okay. It's really
exciting about the book

61
