on Belinda Apple.

65
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:40,800
Her life growing up in England,
education, childhood photos,

66
00:04:40,840 --> 00:04:43,200
articles she wrote for
"Go Fab" magazine before.

67
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:45,800
Well, I don't have any of that.

68
00:04:45,840 --> 00:04:48,700
Idea. Wait! Call her!

69
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:56,600
Right. Or I could do a sort of
rough draft of the foreword for you and then...

70
00:04:56,640 --> 00:05:00,000
I'm sure your knickers are in a knot
about this but look at you.

71
00:05:00,200 --> 00:05:03,600
No offense but you're
sugar-encrusted nobody.

72
00:05:03,640 --> 00:05:05,100
Do you really think Stanson

00:05:05,140 --> 00:05:07,400
