to a book by its biggest star?

73
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:10,000
No.

74
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:12,700
No. "No" is right.

75
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:13,100
Then get me what I need.

76
00:05:13,140 --> 00:05:14,200
Go!

77
00:05:20,300 --> 00:05:22,600
