218
00:13:45,040 --> 00:13:45,900
How do you know?

219
00:13:45,940 --> 00:13:52,400
Yes! Africa! Nola and I have been planning
this trip for ages. It's for a charity...

220
00:13:52,440 --> 00:13:54,100
for children.

221
00:13:54,140 --> 00:13:56,600
Did I mention this is launching
a whole new book division?

222
00:13:56,640 --> 00:14:00,500
Goodness! Gracious me! It's two o'clock
in the morning here. I've got to go to bed.

223
00:14:00,540 --> 00:14:01,800
You two work it out.
I'll talk to you later. Bye!

224
00:14:05,100 --> 00:14:08,200
