229
00:14:15,440 --> 00:14:20,500
Or you're fired. You recommended her.
I don't care if she's boosted circulation 50%.

230
00:14:20,540 --> 00:14:24,100
If she blows this for me I will
destroy her... and you.

231
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:25,700
Have a good night!

232
00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:29,400
